item.description:
The weather is nice on Sunday, tennis anyone? This will be our first tennis event, so we will start small. If you cannot make it this Sunday and are interested in future tennis events - please leave a comment and your level of play.

Next time we will find more courts to accommodate more players. We will volley and maybe play some games. It's an opportunity to meet other tennis players in our Asian meetup group.

group.name: The Greater Boston Asian Professionals Meetup Group

item.name: Tennis - Sunday
